{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24/comments/19084911.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24#comment-19084911"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 24, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable cmake module"}, "content": {"raw": "One note from the [cmake wiki](http://www.cmake.org/Wiki/CMake/Tutorials/How_to_create_a_ProjectConfig.cmake_file) about setting up relocatable config files:\n\n\"On Windows it requires that the variables INSTALL_INCLUDE_DIR and INSTALL_CMAKE_DIR are set to paths with the same drive letter. Otherwise there is no valid relative path connecting the two.\"", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>One note from the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://www.cmake.org/Wiki/CMake/Tutorials/How_to_create_a_ProjectConfig.cmake_file\" rel=\"nofollow\">cmake wiki</a> about setting up relocatable config files:</p>\n<p>\"On Windows it requires that the variables INSTALL_INCLUDE_DIR and INSTALL_CMAKE_DIR are set to paths with the same drive letter. Otherwise there is no valid relative path connecting the two.\"</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-18T22:59:09.860108+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 19084911}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24/comments/19164019.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24#comment-19164019"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 24, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable cmake module"}, "content": {"raw": "@dirk-thomas \n\nI think we'll do the same for sdformat and gazebo as well.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>@dirk-thomas </p>\n<p>I think we'll do the same for sdformat and gazebo as well.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-19T22:55:38.331647+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 19164019}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24/comments/19164030.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24#comment-19164030"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 24, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable cmake module"}, "content": {"raw": "Indeed, for test like this (https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/src/1e2ecb7125ddfc85f12cf327b9fa6d1929603b1d/test/cmake/config-cmake.cc?at=default) the generated CMake code needs to be relocatable in order to test it without installation.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Indeed, for test like this (<a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/src/1e2ecb7125ddfc85f12cf327b9fa6d1929603b1d/test/cmake/config-cmake.cc?at=default\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/src/1e2ecb7125ddfc85f12cf327b9fa6d1929603b1d/test/cmake/config-cmake.cc?at=default</a>) the generated CMake code needs to be relocatable in order to test it without installation.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-19T22:57:27.166986+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Dirk Thomas", "uuid": "{a8effe61-90f2-4949-89a8-9c6972071de7}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Ba8effe61-90f2-4949-89a8-9c6972071de7%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Ba8effe61-90f2-4949-89a8-9c6972071de7%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f77876936467715bd75258c967bcaa4d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsDT-2.png"}}, "nickname": "Dirk Thomas", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:763d049c-c4c6-4e59-85a5-2d7a8fbbdd58"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 19164030}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24/comments/21044794.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24#comment-21044794"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 24, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable cmake module"}, "content": {"raw": "I think catkin provides an example of a relocatable config file:\n\n* https://github.com/ros/catkin/blob/indigo-devel/cmake/templates/pkgConfig.cmake.in#L94-L110", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I think catkin provides an example of a relocatable config file:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ros/catkin/blob/indigo-devel/cmake/templates/pkgConfig.cmake.in#L94-L110\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/ros/catkin/blob/indigo-devel/cmake/templates/pkgConfig.cmake.in#L94-L110</a></li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-08-20T00:26:44.672023+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 21044794}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24/comments/22756020.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24#comment-22756020"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/24.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 24, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable cmake module"}, "content": {"raw": "Interesting discussion on the CMake mailing list on how to write a relocatable cmake module for a library with dependencies : http://public.kitware.com/pipermail/cmake/2015-October/061761.html .", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Interesting discussion on the CMake mailing list on how to write a relocatable cmake module for a library with dependencies : <a href=\"http://public.kitware.com/pipermail/cmake/2015-October/061761.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">http://public.kitware.com/pipermail/cmake/2015-October/061761.html</a> .</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-10-25T00:44:22.104834+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Silvio Traversaro", "uuid": "{34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:e1c3e6a0-9a64-4e5f-a668-feebc191c5b6/578caaa1-056c-45a2-8bf9-bee94c3bebef/128"}},